{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017EjLV3bHLj2qLruM42KuG3","type":"tool_result","content":"260\t- `flow` — ordered execution steps with `loop:` blocks for feedback loops\n261\t- Task properties: `scope` (per-story/per-run), `session` (fresh/continue), `source_access` (boolean), `agent` (agent name)\n262\t\n263\t### Agent Configuration Format\n264\t\n265\tBMAD-compatible base fields (required) with optional PersonaNexus-compatible traits:\n266\t\n267\t```yaml\n268\tname: evaluator\n269\trole:\n270\t  title: Adversarial QA Evaluator\n271\t  purpose: Exercise the built artifact and determine if it actually works\n272\tpersona:\n273\t  identity: Senior QA who trusts nothing without evidence\n274\t  communication_style: Blunt, evidence-first\n275\t  principles:\n276\t    - Never give the benefit of the doubt\n277\t    - Every PASS requires evidence\n278\t# Optional: quantified personality\n279\tpersonality:\n280\t  traits:\n281\t    rigor: 0.98\n282\t    directness: 0.95\n283\t    warmth: 0.2\n284\t```\n285\t\n286\t### Multi-Level Configuration\n287\t\n288\t```\n289\t# Embedded (inside codeharness package)\n290\ttemplates/agents/     # 8 BMAD + evaluator\n291\ttemplates/workflows/  # default sprint workflow\n292\t\n293\t# User-level\n294\t~/.codeharness/agents/      # personal agent customizations\n295\t~/.codeharness/workflows/   # personal workflows\n296\t\n297\t# Project-level\n298\t.codeharness/agents/        # project agent patches or custom agents\n299\t.codeharness/workflows/     # project workflow patches or custom workflows\n300\t```\n301\t\n302\tResolution: embedded → user patch → project patch (sequential merge). Patches use `extends: embedded://name` with structured `overrides:` and freeform `prompt_patches:`.\n303\t\n304\t### Installation & Setup\n305\t\n306\t```bash\n307\tnpm install -g codeharness\n308\tclaude plugin install codeharness\n309\tcodeharness init    # detect stack, generate default workflow"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01FLHeMC7z4edzYfkx1nRfuA","session_id":"fb9c1538-17c2-48c5-8d63-6a9f60fb8dd3","uuid":"1eafdef4-bd0c-4919-b787-3d1aa7baee97","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:12:46.543Z"}
