idateAgent internal variable naming clarity","+- disallowedTools could benefit from minItems: 1 (debatable)","+","+**Coverage:** 96.65% overall, schema-validate.ts at 100%.","+","+## Token Report","+- Total tool calls: 18","+- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 5, Edit: 7, Grep: 1, Glob: 1, Skill: 1","+- Largest Bash outputs: vitest verbose (~40 lines), codeharness coverage (~5 lines), git diff (~25 lines)","+- Files read: 7 unique, 7 total reads","+- Redundant operations: Coverage command ran twice","+"," ### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — dev-story (2026-04-02T15:18)"," "," None."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
