ated by subagent:** Per instruction, subagent did not modify sprint-status.yaml. Orchestrator handles status transitions.\n- **No project-context.md found:** Only templates exist. No material impact.\n- **Observations:** All 8 ACs are `test-provable` — purely schema definition + validation function story.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 19\n- By tool: Read: 9, Grep: 5, Glob: 4, Bash: 1, Write: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `git log --oneline -10` (~10 lines)\n- Files read: 12 unique, 13 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n\n### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — code-review (2026-04-02T15:24)\n\n**Bugs found:**\n- MEDIUM: Schema accepted empty strings for name, role.title, role.purpose, persona.identity, persona.communication_style, principles items — fixed with minLength: 1\n- MEDIUM: Schema accepted empty principles array — fixed with minItems: 1\n- MEDIUM: Schema accepted personality: {} without traits — fixed by making traits required\n- MEDIUM: Tests missing for empty string, personality without traits, empty principles, non-string disallowedTools — all added\n\n**Code quality issues NOT fixed (LOW):**\n- validateAgent internal variable naming clarity\n- disallowedTools could benefit from minItems: 1 (debatable)\n\n**Coverage:** 96.65% overall, schema-validate.ts at 100%.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 18\n- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 5, Edit: 7, Grep: 1, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: vitest verbose (~40 lines), codeharness coverage (~5 lines), git diff (~25 lines)\n- Files read: 7 unique, 7 total reads\n- Redundant operations: Coverage command ran twice\n\n### 3-1-agent-config-json-schema — dev-story (2026-04-02T15:18)\n\nNone.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 14\n- By tool: Bash: 5, Read: 4, Edit: 5, Write: 2, Glob: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npx vitest run` full suite (~500+ lines), `npx tsc --noEmit` (~3 lines)\n- Files read: 5 unique, 5 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":